234
00:11:36,612 --> 00:11:39,761
un hot, hob ikh gemuzt ales onfirn.

235
00:11:40,037 --> 00:11:42,090
kh'hob gebroykht tsu oyfshteyn um

236
00:11:42,670 --> 00:11:44,413
dray far togs

237
00:11:44,413 --> 00:11:48,075
biz oyf der nakht bin ikh keseyder arumgelofn oyf di fis

238
00:11:48,075 --> 00:11:49,042
un gearbet.

239
00:11:49,470 --> 00:11:51,033
khuts

240
00:11:51,192 --> 00:11:55,286
di erd, hot ir gehat oykh andere, hot ir gehat

241
00:11:54,280 --> 00:11:57,261
velder, vald vos m'hot gemakht holts

242
00:11:57,368 --> 00:11:59,927
vorn a mol hot men geheytst mit holts.

243
00:12:00,135 --> 00:12:02,410
m'hot nisht geheytst mit UNK vi haynt

244
00:12:02,410 --> 00:12:03,622
mit GAS.

245
00:12:03,696 --> 00:12:06,947
un deys holts hot men gebroykht geyn in vald arayn shnaydn

246
00:12:07,037 --> 00:12:08,987
un ibernemen

247
00:12:08,987 --> 00:12:11,387
un aheymbrengen. dos iz vayt geven

248
00:12:11,387 --> 00:12:13,957
s'hot gekent zayn vayt fun der hoyz

249
00:12:14,412 --> 00:12:15,941
akht, tsen mayl

250
00:12:16,977 --> 00:12:20,888
un dos ⟨flegn⟩ mir geyn un aheymbrengen un d- z- ibernemen

251
00:12:20,888 --> 00:12:22,643
hot dos gebroykht alts arbet.

252
00:12:22,643 --> 00:12:24,227
dos ales hob ikh gemakht.

253
00:12:24,925 --> 00:12:29,576
ir hot gearbet oyf der erd aleyn, oder ir flegt onnemen arbeter?

254
00:12:29,464 --> 00:12:34,875
n- aleyn hobn mir nisht gekent azoy fil erd baarbetn, hobn mir gemuzt nemen hilf. UNK m'hot gedungen

255
00:12:35,370 --> 00:12:36,793
m'hot gedungen

256
00:12:36,793 --> 00:12:41,020
ferd un aker vegele. m'hot ge- vayl s'iz nisht geven keyn traktorn

257
00:12:41,020 --> 00:12:42,446
hot men mit ferd

258
00:12:42,446 --> 00:12:43,565
geakert

259
00:12:43,858 --> 00:12:46,788
un mit oksn, un azoy hot men gelebt.

260
00:12:48,280 --> 00:12:50,754
kent ir undz dertseyln, gedenkt ir, vegn

261
00:12:50,760 --> 00:12:54,343
groyse yidishe yontoyvim? vi flegt bay aykh forkumen. tsum bayshpil

262
00:12:54,343 --> 00:12:57,605
kent ir dertseyln vegn peysekh vos fleg bay aykh forkumen?

263
00:12:57,747 --> 00:13:02,702
peysekh iz geven, yeder balebos hot zikh avekgeleygt veyts

264
00:13:02,927 --> 00:13:04,355
oyf peysekh

265
00:13:04,395 --> 00:13:06,785
un m'iz geganen dos aleyn moln

266
00:13:06,943 --> 00:13:08,096
un aleyn

267
00:13:08,096 --> 00:13:09,063
gezupt

268
00:13:10,015 --> 00:13:12,017
un aleyn gebakn

269
00:13:12,597 --> 00:13:16,961
un azoy hot men aheymgebrengt matses oyf peysekh, hot zikh aleyn gemakht ales.

270
00:13:17,254 --> 00:13:18,497
un

271
00:13:18,604 --> 00:13:24,960
UNK peysekh hot men shoyn gekoyft m'hot gebroykht peysekhdike zakhn. vos nisht hot men ales aleyn gemakht.

272
00:13:25,253 --> 00:13:27,342
a bayshpil, m'hot gebroykht shtark.

273
00:13:27,342 --> 00:13:28,655
veys vos heyst shtark?

274
00:13:29,674 --> 00:13:30,995
fun kartofl.

275
00:13:30,995 --> 00:13:32,486
hot men aleyn gemakht.

276
00:13:32,863 --> 00:13:34,949
mit dem hot men gemakht gebeks.

277
00:13:35,243 --> 00:13:37,481
m'hot alege- aleyn gehat honik

278
00:13:37,521 --> 00:13:41,255
tsuker hot men gezen tsu farshafn peysekhdik. s'iz shver geven.

279
00:13:41,255 --> 00:13:42,462
zalts

280
00:13:42,462 --> 00:13:45,564
hot men genumen, a groysn shteyn hot men gekoyft.

281
00:13:45,604 --> 00:13:48,247
m'hot dos arumgeklapt fun oysvendik

282
00:13:48,540 --> 00:13:50,806
un ⟨ot do⟩ inevendik vos iz geven

283
00:13:50,806 --> 00:13:54,975
vos iz reyn geven, dos hot men genumen oyf peysekh tseklapt un tseribn

284
00:13:54,975 --> 00:13:56,094
me zol nitsn

285
00:13:56,353 --> 00:13:57,877
f- zalts oyf peysekh.

286
00:13:57,877 --> 00:14:01,275
un azoy iz gegangen di gantse lebn. ales hot men gemakht mit di hent.

287
00:14:01,230 --> 00:14:04,092
ir meynt alts zol zayn kosher lepeysekh?

288
00:14:03,188 --> 00:14:07,817
ales zayn kosher lepeysekh. zol zayn, UNK ⟨aropgehitn vern⟩ UNK ales aleyn gemakht.

289
00:14:07,817 --> 00:14:09,999
m'hot aleyn gekalkht. m'hot aleyn

290
00:14:10,208 --> 00:14:11,214
geroymt.

291
00:14:11,220 --> 00:14:12,969
m'hot tsugenumen hilf

292
00:14:13,077 --> 00:14:15,062
ober ales hot men aleyn gemakht.

293
00:14:17,700 --> 00:14:21,626
kent ir undz dertseyln vi flegt bay aykh forkumen der seyder

294
00:14:22,290 --> 00:14:24,747
oyf peysekh? gedenkt ir?

295
00:14:23,455 --> 00:14:25,839
der seyder iz forgekumen

296
00:14:25,839 --> 00:14:29,979
m'hot, nokh m'hot opgedavnt mit minyen in, in di shul

297
00:14:30,272 --> 00:14:34,164
hot men UNK nokh minyen iz men aheymgeganen, un ⟨m'hot men⟩ gemakht dem seyder.

298
00:14:34,170 --> 00:14:38,855
s'hot gedoyert biz um eyns, tsvey bay nakht, um draye, ven vi azoy.

299
00:14:39,418 --> 00:14:41,842
un azoy hot men ongefirt dem seyder.

300
00:14:42,287 --> 00:14:43,226
geven

301
00:14:42,338 --> 00:14:45,420
a sakh mentshn flegn ⟨zayn⟩ oyfn seyder bay aykh?

302
00:14:45,004 --> 00:14:45,842
alts

303
00:14:46,253 --> 00:14:55,055
di gantse familye. a ⟨fremdn⟩ mentshn iz nisht zeyer geven in yene yorn. yeder hot zikh ⟨gezen⟩ alts tsu geyn aheym oyf peysekh, zol nisht geyn in di fremd.

304
00:14:56,023 --> 00:14:58,762
m'hot nisht gezukht. dos iz nisht, iz zeltn geven

305
00:14:58,762 --> 00:15:04,584
tomer yo geven a, a mol a soldat vos er iz geven in militer. dortn iz geven di grenets

306
00:15:04,584 --> 00:15:06,395
di tshekhishe grenets

307
00:15:06,402 --> 00:15:07,706
hobn mir gehat

308
00:15:07,706 --> 00:15:08,893
a soldat

309
00:15:09,743 --> 00:15:13,567
a, eyn mol denk ikh, un er iz nisht, m'hot im nisht aheymgelozt

310
00:15:13,573 --> 00:15:16,807
hot men, iz er geven bay undz oyfn, di tsvey seyder nakht.

311
00:15:17,117 --> 00:15:19,439
mer ⟨denk⟩ ikh nisht UNK ⟨geven zayn⟩ fremde.

312
00:15:21,927 --> 00:15:26,629
ir zogt az bay aykh zaynen geven tsvey shuln. eyn shul iz gevezn ayer foter's shul.

313
00:15:26,128 --> 00:15:27,354
yo.

314
00:15:27,428 --> 00:15:29,784
UNK ikh meyn a besmedresh.

315
00:15:29,470 --> 00:15:30,274
yo.

316
00:15:30,533 --> 00:15:33,446
di tsveyte shul iz gevezn far vemen?

317
00:15:33,402 --> 00:15:34,746
farn gantsn

318
00:15:34,465 --> 00:15:35,556
far di gants-

319
00:15:34,768 --> 00:15:36,736
far a gantsn dorf.

320
00:15:36,912 --> 00:15:39,234
nor dos iz vayt geven

321
00:15:39,477 --> 00:15:41,477
un m'hot nisht gekent geyn

322
00:15:41,477 --> 00:15:44,317
fun, biz ahin yedn tsu fri un oyf di nakht

323
00:15:44,317 --> 00:15:48,059
vayl s'iz vayt. dos iz geb- geven a tsvey mayl vayt fun

324
00:15:48,201 --> 00:15:52,256
fun eyn yid, fun eyn ek dorf, ⟨vorn⟩ dos dorf iz groys geven

325
00:15:52,256 --> 00:15:54,338
ober tseshpreyt. s'iz nisht geven

326
00:15:54,428 --> 00:15:57,240
geboyt eyns lebn dos andere di hayzer.

327
00:15:57,263 --> 00:15:59,850
s'iz geven do a hoyz, un bay yeder

328
00:15:59,850 --> 00:16:02,060
fir, finef hundert meter a hoyz.

329
00:16:02,060 --> 00:16:06,347
nu, iz vayt geven di shul, hot men, iz bay undz oykh geven a shul

330
00:16:06,347 --> 00:16:09,351
un dort hot men gedavnt tsu fri, un oyf der nakht in yener zayt

331
00:16:09,351 --> 00:16:12,810
mentshn vos zey hobn in yene zay- gegnt gevoynt, hot men dortn gedavnt.

332
00:16:12,810 --> 00:16:14,840
ober shabes un yontev

333
00:16:15,133 --> 00:16:17,692
zenen mir zikh tsamgekumen ale in di groyse shul.

334
00:16:19,774 --> 00:16:22,501
ir hot gehat a rov in der shul?

335
00:16:22,221 --> 00:16:24,864
undz ho'mir gehat a rov in Halmin.

336
00:16:25,444 --> 00:16:29,001
di ale derfer dortn, geven zibn, akht derfer

337
00:16:29,001 --> 00:16:31,411
s'hot ales gekert tsu Halmin.

338
00:16:31,603 --> 00:16:36,423
undz ho'mir nisht gehat keyn ekstern rov vayl mir hobn nisht gekent oyshaltn a rov aleyn.

339
00:16:36,582 --> 00:16:38,837
s'iz geven tsu fil gelt. s'iz shver geven.

340
00:16:40,412 --> 00:16:42,468
der rov flegt kumen tsu aykh ven

341
00:16:42,468 --> 00:16:43,359
in shul?

342
00:16:42,859 --> 00:16:46,194
eyn mol in yor fleg er alts aroyskumen oyf a shabes

343
00:16:47,837 --> 00:16:49,485
fleg der rov alts aroyskumen.

344
00:16:50,132 --> 00:16:52,100
iz ver f- ver flegt bay aykh

345
00:16:52,123 --> 00:16:54,479
shteyn baym omed davenen?

346
00:16:54,452 --> 00:16:57,753
m- mir ho'mir dort geflegt davenen vemen m'hot geshikt.

347
00:16:58,232 --> 00:17:02,276
ven tomer der gabe vemen hot geshikt, a mol hot er dem geshikt, a mol yenem

348
00:17:02,333 --> 00:17:04,875
ver s'hot beser gekent hot men b- mer geshikt.

349
00:17:04,915 --> 00:17:06,984
ir hot a mol gedavnt baym omed?

350
00:17:06,821 --> 00:17:11,995
ikh bin nokh geven a yunger man nokh. a yungen man hot men nisht gelozt davenen, nor a f- a farheyratn.

351
00:17:13,683 --> 00:17:14,735
haynt

352
00:17:13,808 --> 00:17:18,611
gede- gedenkt ir vos iz mit aykh forgekumen ven ir zayt gevorn bar mitsve?

353
00:17:18,869 --> 00:17:22,638
ikh bin geven bar mitsve, hot men mir, mir gemakht a sheyne bar mitsve.

354
00:17:22,638 --> 00:17:24,533
m'hot gerufn dem gantsn oylem.

355
00:17:24,827 --> 00:17:26,610
kh'hob geha- s'iz geven

356
00:17:26,633 --> 00:17:29,439
mayner a feter, dem tatn's a shvoger

357
00:17:29,439 --> 00:17:30,862
oykh geven a rov

358
00:17:31,003 --> 00:17:34,237
in ⟨Mizhe⟩. er iz oykh dort geven oyf mayn bal mitsve

359
00:17:34,547 --> 00:17:37,395
zol basheynen, un m'hot gemakht a sheyne sude.

360
00:17:37,395 --> 00:17:41,915
un m- dos iz, un ale zenen gekumen. ⟨dem gantsn⟩ dorf iz gekumen tsu der sude.

361
00:17:42,900 --> 00:17:46,910
UNK in shul vos iz gevezn? m'hot aykh gerufn tsu di toyre?

362
00:17:47,332 --> 00:17:48,332
tsu vos?

363
00:17:48,210 --> 00:17:49,290
tsu di toyre?

364
00:17:49,465 --> 00:17:50,674
tsu leyen-

365
00:17:49,820 --> 00:17:53,022
yo. ven ikh bin bar mitsve gevorn, hob ikh alts oyle geven, nokh

366
00:17:53,022 --> 00:17:55,064
far di bar mitsve hob ikh shoyn oyle geven

367
00:17:55,064 --> 00:17:58,802
vos a yingl hot gemegt oyle zayn far di bar mitsve.

368
00:17:58,802 --> 00:18:00,478
a bayshpil. mafter

369
00:18:00,940 --> 00:18:03,600
fleg ikh bay di nayn yor shoyn oyle zayn.

370
00:18:03,758 --> 00:18:05,051
un

371
00:18:05,985 --> 00:18:08,631
khag begalile

372
00:18:08,631 --> 00:18:10,164
dos fleg men mikh oft

373
00:18:10,862 --> 00:18:11,733
gebn.

374
00:18:12,145 --> 00:18:15,514
s'iz geven a groyser yikhes ver es hot gehat in yene yorn

375
00:18:16,768 --> 00:18:19,563
un ven ikh ⟨bin⟩ bar mitsve gevorn, hob ikh shoyn oyle geven

376
00:18:19,620 --> 00:18:22,081
ven me, ven UNK iz oysgekumen

377
00:18:22,081 --> 00:18:23,158
farshidns.

378
00:18:24,531 --> 00:18:27,771
kent ir mir dertseyln vegn di batsiungen tsvishn

379
00:18:27,771 --> 00:18:29,121
aykh yidn

380
00:18:29,121 --> 00:18:32,551
un di nisht yidn vos hobn gelebt in ayer dorf?

381
00:18:32,378 --> 00:18:33,556
s'iz geven

382
00:18:33,556 --> 00:18:37,232
nisht gring. s'iz shver geven. alts hot men geshrign

383
00:18:37,542 --> 00:18:40,686
JIDAN LA PALESTINA

384
00:18:40,686 --> 00:18:43,138
di yidn zoln geyn oyf Palestine

385
00:18:43,347 --> 00:18:45,383
nisht ts- s'iz nisht zeyer plats do

386
00:18:45,456 --> 00:18:50,057
un ale, tomer hot a yid epes gemakht, hot men gez- alts gezogt "di yidn."

387
00:18:50,755 --> 00:18:52,774
zey hobn alts gezukht di yidn

388
00:18:53,303 --> 00:18:54,734
tsu unterdrikn

389
00:18:54,734 --> 00:18:56,739
undz ontsuton tsores

390
00:18:56,880 --> 00:18:58,527
az a

391
00:18:58,618 --> 00:18:59,827
baamter

392
00:19:00,289 --> 00:19:01,247
funem

393
00:19:01,247 --> 00:19:03,202
shtot hoyz oder

394
00:19:03,630 --> 00:19:05,070
fun di SCHOOL

395
00:19:05,070 --> 00:19:07,033
oder der galekh

396
00:19:07,545 --> 00:19:12,072
⟨azoy vi er iz⟩ durkhgegangen, hot men gemuzt heybn dem hut in der heykh un zikh bukn tsun im

397
00:19:12,072 --> 00:19:13,209
un grisn

398
00:19:13,317 --> 00:19:14,644
tomer nisht

399
00:19:14,785 --> 00:19:16,376
hot men im genumen

400
00:19:16,376 --> 00:19:22,085
un m'hot im ge—afirgenumen mayne eltern UNK zey tuen mikh nisht edukirn

401
00:19:22,159 --> 00:19:24,093
zey gebn mir nisht keyn edukatsye.

402
00:19:23,627 --> 00:19:25,815
dos iz in velkhe shprakh, in rumenish?

403
00:19:25,416 --> 00:19:26,743
in rumenish.

404
00:19:28,588 --> 00:19:32,564
m'hot getsitert far zey. m'hot zey gezen, hot men getsitert.

405
00:19:34,393 --> 00:19:37,173
beys ir hot gelernt in shul, ir hot geler-

406
00:19:37,173 --> 00:19:39,383
geendikt in velkhe shul, in velkhe shprakh?

407
00:19:39,270 --> 00:19:41,820
in rumenishe shprakh hob ikh geendikt di shul.

408
00:19:41,599 --> 00:19:43,854
iz gevezn a yidishe shul dortn?

409
00:19:43,557 --> 00:19:45,171
neyn, nor a kheyder.

410
00:19:45,582 --> 00:19:47,483
dos heyst, azoy vi a shul

411
00:19:48,180 --> 00:19:50,334
iz zi geven ekstere. dos hot men

412
00:19:50,593 --> 00:19:53,439
ven mir hobn nisht gebroykht in di shul, zenen mir gegangen in kheyder.

413
00:19:54,492 --> 00:19:57,591
zogt mir, vos iz forgekumen in ayer lebn shpeter.

414
00:19:57,765 --> 00:20:00,796
ersht shoyn gevorn nokh bar- nokh barmitsve

415
00:20:00,820 --> 00:20:04,189
ir hot alts gearbet, zayt ir gevezn in der militer?

416
00:20:04,549 --> 00:20:07,513
nokh di barmitsve bin ikh gan in di yeshive

417
00:20:07,772 --> 00:20:10,736
in r- oyf Halmin. dos iz geven dos ershte.

418
00:20:10,843 --> 00:20:12,963
dort hob ikh gelernt a por yor.

419
00:20:13,324 --> 00:20:14,499
nokh dem

420
00:20:14,674 --> 00:20:18,988
iz dortn geven di tshekhishe grenets, ⟨hot men mikh⟩ aribergeshvertst di grenets.

421
00:20:18,994 --> 00:20:23,881
ikh bin avekgan oyf KASZONY lernen. dos iz geven ⟨a ZIDITSHOYVER⟩ rebe

422
00:20:24,597 --> 00:20:31,054
vos er hot, mayn tate iz geven a groyser khosid fun dem rebn. er iz geven zeyer a tayerer mentsh un a tayerer yid

423
00:20:31,093 --> 00:20:33,854
zikhroyne levrokhe, ikh hob di PICTURES fun im

424
00:20:34,367 --> 00:20:36,673
un dort hob ikh gelernt

425
00:20:37,135 --> 00:20:38,529
shvartserheyt

426
00:20:38,890 --> 00:20:42,579
ikh bin ariber di grenets geshvertst, un tsurik aheymgekumen geshvertst.

427
00:20:42,855 --> 00:20:45,785
nokh dem hob ikh gelernt in Satmer.

428
00:20:46,247 --> 00:20:47,557
hob ikh oykh gelernt.

429
00:20:48,272 --> 00:20:49,324
shpeter

430
00:20:49,324 --> 00:20:52,232
ven di ungern hobn shoyn tsugenumen dey gegnt

431
00:20:52,305 --> 00:20:57,564
hot shoyn nor mayn bruder gelernt dortn. ikh bin shoyn geven in militer. ikh ⟨hob⟩ nisht gelernt.

432
00:20:58,633 --> 00:21:01,226
biz tsum militer hob ikh gelernt in di yeshives.

433
00:21:01,401 --> 00:21:06,187
kent ir dertseyln vi hot men aykh genumen tsu di militer un vi ir hot gedint unter di militer?

434
00:21:05,535 --> 00:21:08,651
mikh hot men genumen tsum militer bay di rumenishe

435
00:21:09,298 --> 00:21:10,456
BEHORDE

436
00:21:10,868 --> 00:21:13,227
bay di tsvontsik yor

437
00:21:13,227 --> 00:21:16,683
un bin ikh geganen forshteyn. vos heyst forshteyn?

438
00:21:16,723 --> 00:21:21,813
di doktoyrim hobn mikh vizitirt un bakukt tsi ikh bin gut far a soldat

439
00:21:22,596 --> 00:21:25,104
un azoy hot men mikh shoyn tsugeteylt

440
00:21:25,228 --> 00:21:27,500
vuhin ikh broykh geyn dinen.

441
00:21:27,658 --> 00:21:30,436
⟨ikh bin⟩ arayngekumen, di tsayt iz gekumen

442
00:21:30,915 --> 00:21:33,153
akht un draysik in may

443
00:21:33,177 --> 00:21:34,808
april, may

444
00:21:34,915 --> 00:21:38,452
hob ikh gebroykht geyn arayn tsum militer mikh meldn

